{
  "chapter": {
    "id": "lxxe:psalms.83",
    "translationId": "lxxe",
    "bookSlug": "psalms",
    "chapterNumber": 83,
    "referenceLabel": "Psalms 83",
    "summary": "Source text for Psalms 83 in Brenton's English Septuagint."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "lxxe:psalms.83.1",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 83,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 83:1",
      "text": "A Song of a Psalm for Asaph. - O God, who shall be compared to thee? be not silent, neither be still, O God.",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:psalms.83.2",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 83,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 83:2",
      "text": "For behold, thine enemies have made a noise; and they that hate thee have lifted up the head.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:psalms.83.3",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 83,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 83:3",
      "text": "Against thy people they have craftily imagined a device, and have taken counsel against thy saints.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:psalms.83.4",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 83,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 83:4",
      "text": "They have said, Come, and let us utterly destroy them out of the nation; and let the name of Israel be remembered no more at all.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:psalms.83.5",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 83,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 83:5",
      "text": "For they have taken counsel together with one consent: they have made a confederacy against thee;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:psalms.83.6",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 83,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 83:6",
      "text": "even the tents of the Idumeans, and the Ismaelites; Moab, and the Agarenes;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:psalms.83.7",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 83,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 83:7",
      "text": "Gebal, and Ammon, and Amalec; the Philistines also, with them that dwell at Tyre.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:psalms.83.8",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 83,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 83:8",
      "text": "Yea, Assur too is come with them: they have become a help to the children of Lot. Pause.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:psalms.83.9",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 83,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 83:9",
      "text": "Do thou to them as to Madiam, and to Sisera; as to Jabin at the brook of Kison.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:psalms.83.10",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 83,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 83:10",
      "text": "They were utterly destroyed at Aendor: they became as dung for the earth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:psalms.83.11",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 83,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 83:11",
      "text": "Make their princes as Oreb and Zeb, and Zebee and Salmana; even all their princes:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:psalms.83.12",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 83,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 83:12",
      "text": "who said, let us take to ourselves the altar of God as an inheritance.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:psalms.83.13",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 83,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 83:13",
      "text": "O my God, make them as a wheel; as stubble before the face of the wind.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:psalms.83.14",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 83,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 83:14",
      "text": "As fire which shall burn up a wood, as the flame may consume the mountains;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:psalms.83.15",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 83,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 83:15",
      "text": "so shalt thou persecute them with thy tempest, and trouble them in thine anger.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:psalms.83.16",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 83,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 83:16",
      "text": "Fill their faces with dishonour; so shall they seek thy name, O Lord.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:psalms.83.17",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 83,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 83:17",
      "text": "Let them be ashamed and troubled for evermore; yea, let them be confounded and destroyed.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:psalms.83.18",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 83,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 83:18",
      "text": "And let them know that thy name is Lord; that thou alone art Most High over all the earth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    }
  ]
}
